by SpacePossum at 2015-06-22T16:41:48Z

the bug was that tags like this:
```
@{inheritdoc test} c
```
became:
```
{@inheritdoc} c
```
and not
```
{@inheritdoc test} c
```

should be fixed now :)
(I ignore fabbot for now, I like the bot but in this case I think my code is fine ;)  )

