by keradus at 2015-07-01T20:54:41Z

one of possible ways:
```bash
git checkout bf37a52
git branch -D master_phpdoc_inline_tag
git checkout -b master_phpdoc_inline_tag
git cherry-pick --no-commit 1502492
git commit --amend
git cherry-pick ac1fda8
git diff origin/master_phpdoc_inline_tag HEAD
## if no differences then:
git push --force
```

